## üé® Design Features

- **Color Theme**: MHI Black & White (Professional, minimalist)
- **Background**: Deep black (#1A1A1A)
- **Text**: White (#FFFFFF) and light grey (#D0D0D0)
- **Interactive Elements**: 
  - Team member cards with modal popups
  - Service tabs with expandable accordions
  - Training program accordions
  - Smooth animations and transitions

## üìã Page Structure

### Home Page (index.html)
- Hero section with field photo background
- Quick overview of organization
- Statistics cards
- Call-to-action buttons
- Navigation to other pages

### About Us (about.html)
- Organization mission and vision
- Why We Exist section
- Key principles and approach

### Programs (programs.html) ‚ú® INTERACTIVE
- Tabbed interface: Strategy | M&E | Fundraising | Data | Org Dev
- Each tab contains expandable accordion items
- Smooth expand/collapse animations
- Click tab to view services in that category

### Impact (impact.html)
- Statistics and reach information
- Community impact metrics
- Stories and testimonials

### Stories (stories.html)
- Impact stories from field work
- Case studies from partner organizations
- Photos and detailed narratives

### Team (team.html) ‚ú® INTERACTIVE
- 5 founder cards in responsive grid
- Click any card to open detailed modal with:
  - Full photo
  - Complete bio
  - Expertise areas
  - LinkedIn button
- Keyboard accessible (Tab, Enter, Escape)
- Mobile responsive

### Training (training.html) ‚ú® INTERACTIVE
- 4 training program categories (Workshops, Internships, Courses, Fellowships)
- Expandable accordion items
- Program descriptions and eligibility
- Call to action to contact

### Contact (contact.html)
